    <p>
        The goal of Rhapsody is to provide a simple yet powerful starting point. It handles the boilerplate and provides
        essential tools without imposing a rigid structure, giving you the freedom to build your application your way.
        We believe in clean code, modern PHP features, and a great developer experience.
    </p>
